    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ToolTreaux deluxe set of wax carvers features 7 different double-ended spatula tools for a variety of crafting uses like sculpting, carving, picking, jewelry making, make up special effects and more. Each set comes with 14 assorted tips that make the ultimate set of multi-tools for precision work crafting projects.These spatula tools are constructed of durable, high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust, making them ideal for use with both wet and dry mediums. The corrosion-resistant material will ensure a long life for your tools (just make sure to wipe them clean and dry them before you put them away).Originally designed for precision work, these craft-specific pick tools are great for cleaning small parts, carving wax, creating designs, modeling, molding and smoothing</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux Stainless Steel Wax Carver Spatula Tip Pick Crafting Tool Kit</h2>\n  <p>The ToolTreaux deluxe set of wax carvers features 7 different double-ended spatula tools for a variety of crafting uses like sculpting, carving, picking, jewelry making, make up special effects and more. Each set comes with 14 assorted tips that make the ultimate set of multi-tools for precision work crafting projects.These spatula tools are constructed of durable, high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust, making them ideal for use with both wet and dry mediums. The corrosion-resistant material will ensure a long life for your tools (just make sure to wipe them clean and dry them before you put them away).Originally designed for precision work, these craft-specific pick tools are great for cleaning small parts, carving wax, creating designs, modeling, molding and smoothing. Some recommended mediums for spatula pick tools are ceramics, jewelry and clay. Featuring gripped handles, these tools are shaped for comfort and balance to prevent slippage during use, protecting your hands from the picks. Each tool measures about 6.5” in length, and the entire set will easily fit inside most standard tool boxes and craft storage containers. We’ve also included a PVC storage pouch to keep them all safe and organized when not in use.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>DOUBLE-ENDED ASSORTED TIPS - 7pc set of wax carvers have different double-sided spatula tools for a variety of uses like carving, picking, sculpting, jewelry making, make up and special effects. 14 different tips make up; set of multi-tools for any crafting project requiring precision work</li>\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Wax carver spatulas are made of high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust, making it ideal for use with both wet and dry mediums. Corrosion-resistant material ensures a long life for your toolsDouble Ended Spatula &amp; Wax Carving Tools</li>\n    <li><strong>VERSATILE CRAFTING TOOLS - Originally designed for precision work, these craft-specific pick tools are great for carving wax, cleaning small parts, creating designs, molding, modeling, and smoothing. Ideal mediums:</strong> ceramics, jewelry, clay and electronics</li>\n    <li>ERGONOMIC HANDLES - Featuring gripped handles, these tools are shaped for balance and comfort to prevent slippage during use. Measuring 6.75” in length, entire set will easily fit inside most standard tool boxes and craft storage containers</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - 7pc set; Assorted tips:</strong> 14 (double-sided); Material: stainless steel: Handle style: ergonomic grip: Dimensions: 6.5” x .6” x .6”; Color: chrome; PVC storage pouch included</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/multi-tools/7pc-spatula-set-1.jpg\" alt=\"The ToolTreaux deluxe set of wax carvers features 7 different double-ended spatula tools for a variety of crafting uses like sculpting, carving\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 7PWCSS-517</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 154376638081</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Chrome</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ToolTreaux deluxe set of wax carvers features 7 different double-ended spatula tools for a variety of crafting uses like sculpting, carving, picking, jewelry making, make up special effects and more. Each set comes with 14 assorted tips that make the ultimate set of multi-tools for precision work crafting projects.These spatula tools are constructed of durable, high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust, making them ideal for use with both wet and dry mediums. The corrosion-resistant material will ensure a long life for your tools (just make sure to wipe them clean and dry them before you put them away).Originally designed for precision work, these craft-specific pick tools are great for cleaning small parts, carving wax, creating designs, modeling, molding and smoothing.",
